text: Highway 13 (British Columbia Highway 13) is a provincial highway in Aldergrove in the province of British Columbia. Its north end is at a junction with Highway 1 and its south end is at the Aldergrove Border Crossing. Most of Highway 13 is sometimes known as 264th Street.
